00:02:41.370 --> 00:02:44.328
so I asked my mom if
I could join them.

00:02:44.328 --> 00:02:46.293
And she asked the coach.

00:02:46.293 --> 00:02:46.793
Yeah.

00:02:46.793 --> 00:02:49.258
So that's how I
started swimming.

00:02:49.258 --> 00:02:51.230
But everything else is the same.

00:02:51.230 --> 00:02:52.216
THERESA GOH: Similar.

00:02:52.216 --> 00:02:54.188
Same thing, but different.

