And what was the other one?

00:46:00.886 --> 00:46:04.102
AUDIENCE: How to replicate
the success of swimming.

00:46:04.102 --> 00:46:05.185
THERESA GOH: I don't know.

00:46:05.185 --> 00:46:06.727
YIP PIN XIU: I feel
I want to try it.

00:46:06.727 --> 00:46:08.226
THERESA GOH: Yeah,
swimming, I think

00:46:08.226 --> 00:46:10.650
we can achieve a lot more
